node.text:
@panthepack 
#THEPACK 
Album 💽 OUT NOW❗️
.
LINK IN BIO
.
Physical album dropping on September 19th, 12:00 CST
.
实体专辑 9月 19 号 12:00 点 💽
.
PANTHEPACK
Pandas exploring, hoping to pan the taste/standard of music for the next generation.
Something i have been wanting to do
It took about a year and a half for me while every other schedules were in the way to launch this rocket, being patient and making sure everything is set for release.

TEAM WANG has only one standard.
Taste/ flavor and the CHARACTER.
@jsheonofficial @ice.k1ng @itskarencici 
Them three as artist themselves , too talented and  they just shine brighter than the star. I respect them a lot, they are good musicians , and good human beings.
THEY ARE THE ONE.
Magic.

Thank you to all the people that supports me on what I do, walked side by side with me along this crucial journey.
i know the toughness will just add on the further i go.
Thank you for understanding and believing in me.
Like i always say it, I hope I can make you all proud.

Just doing the things i love. Doing things that i would want to see existing in the industry. These are the things that excites me.
I hope i can being you all joy and produce good products to you all.
Trust me. Got so much to say, i guess i will say it in the physical album.
This is PANTHEPACK.
This is Jackson Wang.
Know yourself, make your own history.
TEAM WANG

This is
PANTHEPACK: “The Pack” album

.
我是 王嘉尔 Jackson
我们是PANTHEPACK
4只熊猫在探索阶段，尽我们所能可以用我们的作品输出给未来一代，音乐的品味和标准，
这也是我一直以来都想做的事情。
花了一年半的时间。虽然中途因为其他的计划也在进行，但最终我们还是做了。
等官宣的这一天，等了很久了。

TEAM WANG只有一个标准。
无论你是歌手、舞者… 等等
标准就是：你的味道，你的标签，你自己独特的角色，你的颜色，你的范儿。

谢谢你们在这段旅程中和我一起打拼。跟我一起见证顺利与不顺利。但我知道我坚持，能让我们走得更远。遇到困难，不顺利其实我们从中能学习到很多，并且能让我们变得更强。
谢谢你们对我输出的作品有信任。也支持我一直以来的态度。
就像我一直说的那样，我希望我能让你们骄傲。

每次我产出任何的作品，我希望你们都能感受到我的作品。
希望你们可以体验到。我也经常说，我很简单的，做自己爱的事，相信的事，做好事，做好作品，不浪费时间，希望可以做到属于我们自己的历史。

@jsheonofficial @ice.k1ng @itskarencici 
真的很有天赋的artist。
抛开一切：我很尊重他们，除了专业角度，他们也是很好的人。
就是他们了。

做我喜欢，相信，热爱的事。
做我想在这个行业中看到的事。
希望自己能用作品为大家带来快乐，
让你们骄傲
相信我.
还有很多话没说，专辑里说吧。
这是PANTHEPACK.
这是我 王嘉尔Jackson Wang
Know yourself, make your own history.
TEAM WANG
.
这是
PANTHEPACK: “The Pack” album
.
@teamwang 
#PANTHEPACK 
#TEAMWANG
